quran[9]{c,v,t}:
  16,94,"Ne mulakhola okhwitsuba khwenyu okhuba khwokhukatania hakari wenyu tawe. Eshilenje shiletsa shiarerekha nishibeele nishimalile okhwema obulai muno, mana mupile amabii kenyu khulwa okhwikalila injila ya Nyasaye, mwanyoola eshinyasio eshikhongo."
  16,95,"Ne mulakula shiobukusi obutiti khumalako ka Nyasaye tawe. Eshili ewa Nyasaye nishio eshilayi khwinywe, nikali mbu mwakhamanya."
  16,96,"Ebiamuli ninabio biliwa, ne ebili wa Nyasaye nibo bilitong’a, ne toto efwe khulihelesia balia befwila omurungo kwabu khumalayi kabu kabakholanga."
  16,97,"Yesiyesi ukhola amalayi abe omusatsa nohomba omukhasi, naye nali omusuubili, khwitsa toto okhumumenyia obulamu obulayi, ne toto khulibarunga omurungo kwabu khumalayi kabu kabakholanga."
  16,98,"Ne niwenya okhusoma Ikurani, wilinde khu Nyasaye okhurulana nende Shetani owalondwa."
  16,99,"Toto ye abula amaani khubalia basuubila, mana besikanga Nyasaye wabu Omulesi."
  16,100,"Amaani kaye kali khubalia abamwaambanga obulina, nende balia abamutsokaasinjia nende Nyasaye."
  16,101,"Ne nikhukalukhania olunyali habundu wolunyali, ne Nyasaye ni umanyile muno akayeshinjia, baboola mbu: “Ewe olisa omuchishi.” Halali abanji mubo shibamanyile tawe."
  16,102,"Boola mbu: “Roho woluyali yakeshia okhurula khu Nyasaye wuwo Omulesi khubwatoto, kho katinyisie balia basuubila, ne kabe obulunjifu nende kokhurera akomwikhoyo khubasalamu."